1
00:00:17,079 --> 00:00:18,679
What? You wanna take back your move again?

2
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:21,640
No way, you've taken back too many moves already.

3
00:00:22,320 --> 00:00:22,800
Chu Feng.

4
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:23,760
This game today,

5
00:00:23,760 --> 00:00:24,879
let me teach you a lesson.

6
00:00:24,879 --> 00:00:26,239
Don't always focus on winning or losing.

7
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:27,640
Watch the path beneath your feet.

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:28,679
Got it?

9
00:00:28,679 --> 00:00:29,199
Sir,

10
00:00:29,519 --> 00:00:30,120
I'll remember that.

11
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,159
Next time, I'll do better.

12
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:35,000
Just give me another chance.

13
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:36,759
Qin Mo!

14
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:37,359
Qin Mo!

15
00:00:37,479 --> 00:00:38,600
His old condition is acting up.

16
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:39,560
Quick, drink this.

17
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:42,719
Sir,

18
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:44,880
how many times have I told you?

19
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:47,159
You need to make time to see a doctor.

20
00:00:48,479 --> 00:00:49,759
Just an old problem, I'm fine.

21
00:00:49,759 --> 00:00:50,439
That's enough.

22
00:00:50,759 --> 00:00:51,920
Stop bickering, you two.

23
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:53,159
He's a sore loser.

24
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:53,679
Sir,

25
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:54,520
if you're not convinced, let's play another round.

26
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,240
He won't admit defeat.

27
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:55,799
One more round.

28
00:00:56,039 --> 00:00:56,640
Come on, one more game.

29
00:00:56,840 --> 00:00:57,359
One more.

30
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:08,280
Congratulations.

31
00:01:08,599 --> 00:01:09,599
You got into grad school.

32
00:01:10,519 --> 00:01:11,920
Pepper spray.

33
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:12,879
Aren't you always teasing me,

34
00:01:12,879 --> 00:01:14,120
calling me a tomboy?

35
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,120
Do I really need this?

36
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,760
I'd scare off any creeps myself.

37
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:19,319
Better safe than sorry.

38
00:01:19,640 --> 00:01:20,359
That's thoughtful of you.

39
00:01:20,840 --> 00:01:21,400
I'll take it.

40
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:30,920
Chen Hui!

41
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,519
If you're a real man,

42
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,000
let Siqi go.

43
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,760
Come at me if you want to kill someone!

44
00:01:39,079 --> 00:01:40,879
Dying such a dramatic death,

45
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:42,959
you two should be satisfied.

46
00:01:58,719 --> 00:01:59,359
Siqi!

47
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,879
What's the situation on Chu Feng's side?

48
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,680
Arriving shortly.

49
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:35,080
Sir!

50
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:35,719
Squad assembled and ready.

51
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,439
Chief, how's Sun Bo?

52
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:49,439
He was ambushed by Ma Xiaojun.

53
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,319
He didn't make it.

54
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,439
The mission Sun Bo couldn't finish,

55
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,400
we'll finish for him.

56
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:02,120
Pull yourself together, Chu Feng.

57
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,159
Everyone, stay sharp.

58
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:06,520
This is the most critical moment.

59
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:07,800
Just hold on a little longer,

60
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,080
and we can close the net.

61
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,520
And all of you, keep this in mind.

62
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,719
Everyone here

63
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,680
has your back.

64
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,199
Yes, sir!

65
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,080
Sir.

66
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,439
All personnel assembled.

67
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:20,120
Based on drone surveillance,

68
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,159
there are three people inside the building.

69
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,280
Most likely Chen Hui,

70
00:03:22,520 --> 00:03:23,800
Yu Tianfang, and He Siqi.

71
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:24,639
Copy that.

72
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,159
Proceed as planned.

73
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:26,599
Copy that.

74
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:27,639
Everyone,

75
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:28,759
left face!

76
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:30,240
Move out!

77
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:34,280
Left face!

78
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,000
Double time, march!

79
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,199
All units, take positions! All units, take positions!

80
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:45,159
Until you receive the signal,

81
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,759
do not enter the factory.

82
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:48,000
We can't risk harming the hostages.

83
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:49,879
Once the order is given,

84
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:51,680
initiate the rescue operation immediately.

85
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,319
Qin Mo,

86
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,400
don't act on your own.

87
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,120
Don't worry.

88
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,599
I won't get in your way.

89
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:01,719
Move out!

90
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:06,879
All units, listen up.

91
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:08,479
All units, listen up.

92
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,599
Flank them by sectors,

93
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,199
and close in layer by layer.

94
00:04:11,199 --> 00:04:12,120
Use your radios

95
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,759
to report your positions in real time.

96
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:14,879
Your teammates

97
00:04:14,879 --> 00:04:15,879
and backup units

98
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,279
are ready to back you up.

99
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,319
Tighten the perimeter

100
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,720
as much as possible.

101
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:22,120
Tighten the perimeter as much as possible!

102
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,120
Qin Mo!

103
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,319
Get the fire department here, fast!

104
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:53,759
Chu Feng!

105
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,519
Watch out!

106
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:55,920
Dispatch, we need the fire department.

107
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,519
We need support at the West Warehouse.

108
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:26,879
Chen Hui!

109
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,040
There's nowhere to run!

110
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,240
Bet you didn't know this, did you?

111
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,759
We found your son.

112
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,959
Don't you dare bring my son into this!

113
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,600
You worthless piece of trash!

114
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,519
You got your own mentor killed!

115
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,079
Come catch me if you have the guts!

116
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:51,600
Chen Hui,

117
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,920
turn yourself in now,

118
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,360
and you might still get to see your son.

119
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:59,120
I really appreciate your concern.

120
00:06:33,199 --> 00:06:33,800
Chen Hui!

121
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:34,600
Chen Hui!

122
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,639
Drop the gun!

123
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,920
I won't let you get away with this.

124
00:07:04,519 --> 00:07:05,879
Call an ambulance, hurry!

125
00:07:09,399 --> 00:07:10,160
I'm fine.

126
00:07:10,759 --> 00:07:12,120
I'm just a little tired.

127
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:13,519
I want to sleep.

128
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:14,759
Don't sleep!

129
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,240
Stay awake, please!

130
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,759
Think about the happiest moments

131
00:07:19,079 --> 00:07:20,199
we shared together.

132
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,519
Every day I spent with you,

133
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:24,920
I was so happy.

134
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,800
From the resort to the restaurant

135
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:46,240
And then to the butcher shop

136
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,160
I kept doing worse and worse

137
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:50,360
yet you still fell for a loser like me.

138
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:52,199
Only now do I realize

139
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:53,879
I'm the luckiest person alive

140
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:56,199
I used up all my luck

141
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,600
Just to meet you

142
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:00,519
I'm the one who's lucky.

143
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,360
Meeting you

144
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,240
made me realize

145
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:06,160
What true love really is

146
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,959
Love isn't about possession,

147
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:09,120
or control.

148
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,199
It's wanting the absolute best for them,

149
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:14,000
and making them happy.

150
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:16,199
I can't live without you

151
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,560
Silly

152
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:21,600
I'm never going to leave you

153
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,839
After all, I'm

154
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,920
the absolute most

155
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:29,000
badass woman in the world.

156
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,559
No, you can't go in

157
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:48,879
I can't breathe

158
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:50,039
What's wrong?

159
00:08:50,919 --> 00:08:51,960
Come on, take a rest

160
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,600
Just rest for a bit

161
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,240
Watch over her

162
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,279
I'll go get a doctor

163
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,080
Patient has a thigh laceration

164
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:03,799
Severe blood loss

165
00:09:03,799 --> 00:09:04,879
Blood pressure 60 over 30

166
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:05,759
Heart rate 140

167
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,879
O2 sats undetectable

168
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,440
Set up two IV lines.

169
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,519
Four units of red cells and normal saline

170
00:09:10,519 --> 00:09:12,000
One milligram of epinephrine, IV push

171
00:09:13,399 --> 00:09:14,519
Found the femoral artery rupture

172
00:09:15,039 --> 00:09:16,200
Hand me a hemostat, quick!

173
00:09:16,679 --> 00:09:17,840
She's in V-fib! Heart stopped!

174
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:18,799
Blood pressure unreadable.

175
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,159
Get the defibrillator, now!

176
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,360
Alright, everybody clear!

177
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,000
Ready!

178
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,279
Clear, shock!

179
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,159
Where's Qibao?

180
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,720
Where is Qibao?

181
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,559
You're hurt,

182
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,120
you need to rest.

183
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,960
My wife saved my life

184
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:57,960
I have to go see her right now

185
00:09:58,279 --> 00:09:59,840
Come on, take me to her

186
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,279
Let's go!

187
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:07,840
No,

188
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,600
Where is Qibao?

189
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,320
What... what are you doing?

190
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:35,679
Doctor

191
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,279
Doctor

192
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:37,360
How is she?

193
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,559
We did everything we could

194
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,200
I'm sorry

195
00:10:47,799 --> 00:10:48,440
Siqi
